[normal]highlights how the VCSE brings particular expertise in community engagement, responding to the needs of service-users and using volunteers and peers to deliver services 
[normal]http://www.nesta.org.uk/publications/assets/features/networks_that_work_partnerships_for_integrated_care_and_services 
[normal]39[bold] NEF’s report, 
[normal]Public Services Inside Out 
[normal]documents the many ways in which citizens are engaging with public service professionals, in health and social care, housing, childcare, education and criminal justice, to design and deliver activities that meet their needs and deliver better results. 
[normal]http://www.neweconomics.org/publications/entry/public-services-inside-out 
